headline: Garmin Product Launches Test Valuation As Motorsports Momentum Meets Market Expectations
summary: Garmin has launched the Garmin Catalyst 2, a motorsports coaching system with real-time guidance and performance analytics. Additionally, the company introduced the zumo XT3, a rugged motorcycle GPS device with updated safety, routing, and tracking features. These products target motorsports drivers and motorcycle riders looking for more data driven support on and off the track. For investors watching NYSE:GRMN, these launches come as the stock trades around $247.1, with returns of 15.1%...
